SQL_STMT_U.val: SELECT a.Contact_Id, a.Contact_Last_Name, a.Contact_First_Name, a.Contact_Organization_Name, a.Entity_CU_Owner, a.Contact_Phone_Number, a.Contact_Address_Line_1, a.Contact_City, a.Zip_Postal_Code, a.Contact_State_Province_Cd, a.Contact_Country_Cd, a.Contact_Email_Address from contact a inner join profile_user b on contact_id=Entity_id where exists( select profile_code from profile c where c.profile_code=b.profile_code and c.Market_place_Owner_ID = :1) :2 :3 :4 :5 :6
